\id DAN Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h DANIEL 
\toc1 DANIEL 
\toc2 Daniel 
\toc3 Dan 
\mt1 DANIEL  
\mt2 (The Book of Daniel)  
\is1 Daniel Cabu Kawng  
\im Daniel cabu he olcueih cabu la om tih tonghma ol, khokhuen cil, hmalong mangthui kawng khaw a tael. Lamhma kah a boel dongah he Babylon vangsawn ah aka om Hebrew hoel Daniel neh a hui rhoek kawng a thui. Daniel neh a hui rhoek tah Pathen kut dongah uepom la om tih a mih Babylon ah cueihnah a then la a cangpuei. Daniel tah bahoeng cueih tih hlang loh a ming mueh mang khaw boeih a thuicaih thai. Nebuchadnezzar kah hmaihueng khui lamkah khaw Pathen loh Daniel neh a hui rhoek te a khang. Daniel he hlang loh a uet tih phae hamla a taeng dongah Daniel te sathueng khui la a voeih. Tedae Pathen loh Daniel koep a khang. Daniel loh mang a hmuh te Pathen caeltueih loh koep a thuicaih pah. Lunglai boeih aka tu kung tah Pathen ni ti a thui. Ramtloe kah uknah hmuiah aka om a pilnam te Pathen ngaiuepnah neh a hloep.  
\iot Oltlueng Rhoek  
\io1 Babylon kah Daniel kawng \ior 1. 1—6. 28\ior*  
\io1 Daniel kah mangthuinah \ior 7. 1—12. 13\ior*  
\c 1  
